N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 900.6 - Withdrawals of applications

State Regulations

An application made to the Life Care Community Council may, upon written request of the applicant to the commissioner, be withdrawn prior
to a decision by the council at any time without prejudice to
resubmission. Notes
